:427,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","line":443,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","line":447,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","line":471,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","line":485,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","line":641,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","line":897,"embedded":true},{"title":"cos $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}$ sin $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right) \\rbrack$ .\n\n## 练习 9.4(1)\n\n1. 下列复数是否用三角形式来表示的? 为什么?\n\n(1)3π(cos 0.5+i sin 0.5)； (2) $2\\left( {\\sin 1 + \\mathrm{i}\\cos 1}\\right)$ ；\n\n(3) $\\cos {131\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {131\\pi }$ ； (4) $\\sqrt{2}\\left( {\\cos {0.3\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {0.2\\pi }}\\right)$ ；\n\n(5) $- 2\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{4} + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{4}}\\right)$ ； (6) $3\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{5} - \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{5}}\\right)$ .\n\n2. 把下列复数用三角形式表示(用辐角主值):\n\n(1) 3; (2)-2i;\n\n(3) $1 + \\mathrm{i}$ ； (4)-1+ $\\sqrt{3}\\mathrm{i}$ .\n\n## 2 三角形式下复数的乘除运算\n\n现在我们讨论三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式.\n\n设有两个用三角形式表示的复数 ${z}_{1} = r\\left( {\\cos \\alpha  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\alpha }\\right)$ 与 ${z}_{2} = s\\left( {\\cos \\beta  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\beta }\\right)$ ,其中 $r = \\left| {z}_{1}\\right|  \\geq  0, s = \\left| {z}_{2}\\right|  \\geq  0$ ,则\n\nQ\n\n$$\n{z}_{1}{z}_{2} = {rs}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  ;\n$$\n\n$$\n\\frac{{z}_{1}}{{z}_{2}} = \\frac{r}{s}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  \\left( {{z}_{2} \\neq  0}\\right) .\n$$\n\n---\n\n三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式称为棣莫弗公式.\n\n---\n\n![bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","line":969},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","line":1117,"embedded":true}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"faettw","at":1773194788064}},"smart_blocks:03-上海教材md/必修二第9章复数/必修二第9章复数-dollar.md###9.1 复数及其四则运算": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07492646,0.00141346,-0.00949203,-0.01571478,0.03431583,-0.02180447,-0.01582989,-0.02882878,0.042559,-0.00585109,0.01899379,-0.0682809,0.07677402,0.0263268,0.022238,0.00492651,-0.02968442,-0.05543777,-0.05337661,0.01518677,0.07751108,-0.05928556,0.01903302,-0.02926542,0.05894099,0.00823718,0.01913284,-0.01427057,0.00846441,-0.1630367,-0.01450022,0.01233082,0.01568015,0.00879504,0.05909184,-0.01626897,-0.04933919,0.01812934,-0.00873827,0.02662163,-0.03708028,0.04735118,0.03439966,-0.00815793,0.04074536,-0.03284305,0.0686716,-0.0239928,0.05695944,-0.0382099,-0.00253274,-0.0066612,-0.00075586,0.04235541,0.0275898,0.01088868,0.05797759,0.05846712,-0.00494578,0.01921427,0.0458708,0.05840653,-0.22552633,0.05361857,0.04445701,-0.04402611,0.00957216,0.0344493,0.02422039,0.05948595,-0.05988109,-0.0186103,0.00484175,0.04219024,0.00117439,-0.08354477,0.02583753,-0.06474113,-0.02702079,-0.02894712,0.01250083,0.08449998,-0.0150294,-0.02066313,0.00137717,